\frac{\sin(n)}{n}
1
n \rightarrow 0
\sin(n)
\sin(n) = n - \frac{n^3}{3!} +\frac{n^5}{5!}+... 
\frac{\sin(n)}{n} = 1-\frac{n^2}{3!} + \frac{n^4}{5!}+...
\lim_{n\to 0}\frac{\sin(n)}{n} = 1
